## 1. Executive Summary
The Bauta Valve is the architectural "Secret Sauce" of Nyx Sieve. It utilizes five isolated, stateless chambers to ensure that no Personally Identifiable Information (PII) ever leaves the user's local hardware chamber. All processing is handled locally on the device's System on a Chip (SoC) to prevent cloud-based data exposure.

